ive with four semesters worth of ASL instruction? (ASL 1, ASL 2, ASL 3, and ASL 4)  for $79.95?  \nSee \"SuperUSB\" in the ASLUniversity bookstore at: https://lifeprint.com/bookstore/books...\n\nFor free ASL Lessons see:    / billvicars  \nTo learn basic fingerspelling see    • ABC's in ASL: Learn how to Fingerspell!  \n\nAbout your instructor:\nhttp://www.lifeprint.com/asl101/pages...\nWarm regards and love to you all.\nI am grateful for your support.\nDr. Bill\n:)","commandRuns":[{"startIndex":54,"length":25,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwici7qQuOuTAxXHtCsGHeqeOgNIs5b-75XNjpgHygEE_4JJ2g==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0UxTF9ZSG1KeXF4VnJwd1p6cE5ib1lwVUo2UXxBQ3Jtc0ttMXNIV0J1MDh2c2JXMFJlTG9ka05jMjR6aG1FeXR4N20xZEl4UGZZZk5uSVRXVUhZQWlrXzFIVmNjd3hGUHdtUjNqbWdyMFNzSnlhVXA2b1NaMmIxeXFDOUlROHhxS1d0UUF5cUFFYzNVaS1fTHZuTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=BzA6aV3_izM","webPageType":"WEB_PAGE_TYPE_UNKNOWN","rootVe":83769}},"urlEndpoint":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqa0UxTF9ZSG1KeXF4VnJwd1p6cE5ib1lwVUo2UXxBQ3Jtc0ttMXNIV0J1MDh2c2JXMFJlTG9ka05jMjR6aG1FeXR4N20xZEl4UGZZZk5uSVRXVUhZQWlrXzFIVmNjd3hGUHdtUjNqbWdyMFNzSnlhVXA2b1NaMmIxeXFDOUlROHhxS1d0UUF5cUFFYzNVaS1fTHZuTQ\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.Lifeprint.com%2F\u0026v=BzA6aV3_izM","target":"TARGET_NEW_WINDOW","nofollow":true}}}},{"startIndex":166,"length":40,"onTap":{"innertubeCommand":{"clickTrackingParams":"CBIQ040EGAUiEwici7qQuOuTAxXHtCsGHeqeOgNIs5b-75XNjpgHygEE_4JJ2g==","commandMetadata":{"webCommandMetadata":{"url":"https://www.youtube.com/redirect?event=video_description\u0026redir_token=QUFFLUhqbGZjUUJ0aGhJRmFtTGJPR2ZXYzFwTU5nNGhKd3xBQ3Jtc0trTTVuZTFGQW9QajVyQUlrdXlQYS1FdzRoU014cHczX3RpdFRIcmxWYVIxVXRfSC05WWRyTnYzUUxmT2FtcHFaSlZZNXFQZ3hETzN0cERLM1JzRlRkM0dLMDZTeTVDUEljMjZHMThGdnk1bjdJX3JLMA\u0026q=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.payp